00:17:36,260 --> 00:17:38,700
If you've never used it, why
the hell are you using it on me?

290
00:17:38,840 --> 00:17:39,100
Fine.

291
00:17:39,439 --> 00:17:41,079
Then we'll head to the hospital in a bit.

292
00:17:50,979 --> 00:17:51,979
Don't step on my cat.

293
00:17:54,100 --> 00:17:55,500
This kit costs sixty yuan in total.

294
00:17:55,619 --> 00:17:56,779
I won't charge you for labor.

295
00:17:57,060 --> 00:17:58,816
Just remember to pay
for the materials later.

296
00:17:58,840 --> 00:18:00,159
You're taking advantage of me!

297
00:18:00,600 --> 00:18:01,600
You old dog!

298
00:18:02,159 --> 00:18:02,640
Well said.

299
00:18:03,180 --> 00:18:04,180
Wait, wait, wait!

300
00:18:04,640 --> 00:18:06,159
I... I was wrong, okay?

301
00:18:10,659 --> 00:18:11,659
Just wait.

302
00:18:12,479 --> 00:18:12,899
Have...

303
00:18:12,979 --> 00:18:14,819
have you ever done this to anyone before?

304
00:18:15,300 --> 00:18:16,819
I'm not a urologist.

305
00:18:17,079 --> 00:18:19,039
How would I have the
chance to do this to anyone?

306
00:18:19,739 --> 00:18:21,840
You're using me as a guinea pig!

307
00:18:22,079 --> 00:18:23,239
You're already in this state.

308
00:18:23,439 --> 00:18:24,519
Why are you being so picky?

309
00:18:24,779 --> 00:18:25,896
Either wait for it to burst,

310
00:18:25,920 --> 00:18:27,000
and I'll call an ambulance,

311
00:18:27,460 --> 00:18:29,538
so everyone on the bar street knows

312
00:18:29,539 --> 00:18:30,840
why you got hospitalized.

313
00:18:31,279 --> 00:18:32,279
But...

314
00:18:32,399 --> 00:18:33,919
what if you put it in the wrong place?

315
00:18:34,319 --> 00:18:36,279
There's only one place.
How could I get it wrong?

316
00:18:36,560 --> 00:18:38,000
At most, it'll scrape a bit of skin.

317
00:18:38,039 --> 00:18:39,000
Just take some anti-inflammatory
meds and you'll be fine.

318
00:18:39,060 --> 00:18:39,319
But...

319
00:18:39,399 --> 00:18:40,800
what if you break it?

320
00:18:40,960 --> 00:18:41,960
No, no, no.

321
00:18:42,000 --> 00:18:42,579
You... you...

322
00:18:42,800 --> 00:18:43,579
find another way.

323
00:18:43,720 --> 00:18:44,720
Try something else.

324
00:18:45,279 --> 00:18:46,279
Go to the hospital.

325
00:18:48,760 --> 00:18:49,760
No, that won't do either.

326
00:18:51,279 --> 00:18:52,600
Don't you run that shop?

327
00:18:53,500 --> 00:18:55,220
Shouldn't you have plenty of ways?

328
00:18:56,180 --> 00:18:57,180
Well, as for ways...

329
00:18:57,859 --> 00:18:58,859
there is one,

330
00:18:59,939 --> 00:19:01,979
but it might not be any
easier than a catheter.

331
00:19:03,479 --> 00:19:04,639
Are you sure you want to try?

